{"lemma":"تَعْلِيلاتٌ","slug":"تَعْلِيلاتٌ","root":"ع.ل.ل","root_slug":"ع-ل-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ل-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30118"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%92%D9%84%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of عَلَّلَ (ʕallala) (form II); entertainment, diversion, distraction, diverting someone's attention (in a pleasant way, like entertaining)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of عَلَّلَ (ʕallala) (form II); argumentation, justification, motivation, explanation, substantiation"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of عَلَّلَ (ʕallala)."},"ipa":["/taʕ.liːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30118","headword_ar":"تَعْلِيلٌ","root":"El","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"giving to drink after giving to drink."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) See 4. [And see also 1, first sentence.] ―         -b2-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plucking fruit one time after another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ell~`hu bihi","text_ar":"عللّٰهُ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) inf. n. as above (K) [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEil~apN","text_ar":"تَعِلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He diverted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occupied, him"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to render him contented"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K;) namely, a thing, (S, O,) or food, &c., (K, TA,) as, for instance, discourse, and the like; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like as the child is diverted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occupied, with somewhat of food, by which he is rendered contented to be restrained from milk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA. *) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN yuEal~ilu nafosahu bitaEil~apK","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ يُعَلِّلُ نَفْسَهُ بِتَعِلَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one diverts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occupies, himself, so as to render himself contented, with something diverting"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEal~ilN","text_ar":"مُعَلِّلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". And see 5.]       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assigning a cause:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asserting a cause."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL.) [One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ell~`hu bika*aA","text_ar":"عللّٰهُ بِكَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He accounted for it by assigning as the cause such a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he asserted it to be caused by such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}